# Phase 10c / R2-N11 — proptest seed-pinning home.
#
# When a `proptest!` block fails in this crate, proptest writes a
# `<test_name>.txt` file here containing the failing seed; subsequent
# runs replay that seed first so regressions stay pinned across CI
# runs and operator machines. The `.gitignore` carries a negation
# entry so any future files in this directory ARE tracked.
#
# This file just keeps the directory in git history before the first
# failure is encountered.
